      <h3>Gestures</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Solar paws:</strong> Press finger pads to heart, warm for three breaths.</li>
        <li><strong>Tiger Lily arc:</strong> Sweep hand tail-to-head in a gentle arc, exhale on the arc’s peak.</li>
        <li><strong>Resilience tap:</strong> Three soft taps at sternum: tap–tap–rest.</li>
