      <ul>
        <li><strong>Morning warm-pad press:</strong> 3 breaths with Solar paws; whisper “warm to begin.”</li>
        <li><strong>Harvest Lines breath:</strong> Inhale from belly to collarbones along “lines,” exhale down the spine.</li>
        <li><strong>Sunset coil-and-release:</strong> Curl shoulders in on inhale, open on exhale; “shine, then rest.”</li>
      </ul>
